			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Indeed, all knights carried with them a "Mercy blade."  This is a knife about 10" long. Once the knight had an opposing knight on the round, he would unsheath this knife, and place it over the eyeslits of the enemy, and make the other knight cry MERY!  The knight could then be taken back for ransom.
<br />

<br />
This is of course after the development of plate armors.  Medieval knights did things a bit differently.<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=767306" target="_blank" class="postlink"> <img src="http://mysite.verizon.net/vze74fvk/sitebuildercontent/sitebuilderpictures/sigrid.jpg" border="0" />
<br />
